

1. Are used to Locate Web Elements based on HTML tag & attributes on a web page.
2. Using them to perform actions like clicking buttons, entering text, and validating 
the presence of elements. 
3. Locators are static and there return type is 'By'. As locators are present inside Abstract Class called 'By'
4. Locators are of 8 types - 

1 id
2 name
3 class
4 tagName
5 linkText
6 partialLinkText
7 xpath
8 css selector

ex - WebElement sbmtBtn = driver.findElement(By.id("Btn")).click();